  <summary date="2006-11-28T17:35:40Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Internet Tax Nondiscrimination Act - Amends the Internet Tax Freedom Act to: (1) permanently ban taxes on Internet access and on multiple or discriminatory taxes on electronic commerce; and (2) repeal the ban exception for a tax on the sale or use of Internet services that was generally imposed and actually enforced prior to October 1, 1998.</summary>
